#

Deli Pickle Sandwich

5 min
$3.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Lunch

Tags:

QuickEasySnack

Description

A refreshing and crunchy sandwich loaded with pickles and creamy cheese, perfect for a quick snack!

Ingredients

  • sourdough bread: 2 slices
  • cheddar cheese: 2 slices
  • dill pickles: 4 slices
  • lettuce: 1 leaf
  • mayonnaise: 1 tablespoon
  • mustard: 1 teaspoon
